# B122a: stray unused enemy-sprite duplicates. Measured (batch 2026-07-13):
# enemy_sprite()/bestiary load generated/<id>.png (root) and enemy_idle_frames()
# loads generated/enemies/animated/<name>_idle_sheet.png — NOTHING reads
# generated/enemies/<id>.png. These 36 were byte-identical copies of the root
# sprites. `*` never crosses `/`, so the tracked animated/ sheets are untouched.
rpg_game/assets/sprites/generated/enemies/*.png
